org.jcrom.annotations

Annotation Type JcrBaseVersionName


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Target(value=FIELD)
public @interface JcrBaseVersionName
    This annotation is used to mark a field that should store a JCR base version name read from the node.
    Note: this will only be relevant for nodes that use the mix:versionable mixin type. Also note that this will be empty when iterating over older versions.
    Author:
    Olafur Gauti Gudmundsson, Nicolas Dos Santos
